  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3357693/" class="title-link">作者写给仓央嘉措的情书，不适合围观</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3357693"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4669508/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4669508-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4669508/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">卡拉不见太阳</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-06-25"
      class="main-meta">2010-06-25 14:40:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3357693_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  历史写的淡了，就不确凿了，于是就没价值了。 作者就像在写一本网络言情，写着写着就把男主角写成自己臆想中那个温柔多情、倜傥忧郁的完美情人。 只当成作者写给仓央嘉措的情书，她写得越投入，别人拜读的时候越容易起鸡皮疙瘩。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3357693/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
