                曾虑多情损梵行,入山又恐别倾城. 世间安得双全法,不负如来不负卿!<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p12463463-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>

