            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2122889/" class=" " title="菁">菁</a>
                (你问花开几许，我答嫣然安在。)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="30792803">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">世间安得双全法，不负如来不负卿。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-03-07 17:46</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>世间安得双全法，不负如来不负卿。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







